        diverse library of manga titles. It pulls content from the public
        MangaDex API, ensuring you get fast, reliable access to high-quality
        scans and translations contributed by the manga community.
      </p>
      <h2>Is MangaRealm<span class="highlight-red">!</span> Safe?</h2>
      <p>
        Yes, MangaRealm! is completely safe to use. We don’t host any malicious
        ads, we don’t collect personal data, and we don’t require any downloads
        or third-party software. The site is built with clean code and focuses
        purely on the reading experience.
      </p>
      <h2>Legal Notice<span class="highlight-red">!</span></h2>
      <p>
        MangaRealm! does not host any manga content directly. All manga
        displayed on the site is sourced through the official MangaDex API,
        which provides publicly available content uploaded by scanlation groups
        under MangaDex’s guidelines. MangaRealm! functions strictly as a viewer
        interface and respects the rights of original creators and scanlators.
        If any content is flagged or removed on MangaDex, it will no longer
        appear on MangaRealm!.
      </p>
